{"tid":2168240,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"王毅：美國要求聯合國制裁伊朗純屬無理取鬧","createTime":"2020-08-21T15:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T07:38:27.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5f258f1aad8db6f6e8513072a60c29ad01059b68","tid":2168240,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:14:28.000Z","msg":"國務委員兼外長王毅在海南同到訪的巴基斯坦外長庫雷希，舉行戰略對話後共同會見記者，王毅批評，美國要求聯合國安理會啟動對伊朗制裁機制，純屬無理取鬧。他說，美方單方面退出伊朗核協議，但又要行使協議賦予當事方的權利，要求啟動制裁機制，質疑世界公理、國際法權威及美國信譽何在，邏輯荒唐。 王毅說，中方建議，在維護伊核協議有效性的前提下，另辟一個多邊對話平台，各方均可提出自己的關切，就維護地區和平穩定形成新的共識。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2353691\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2353691&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThj632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=ed120385\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2353691</a>"},{"pid":"1350e751bb3f3c56bd914a15376fd7bcd45165ce","tid":2168240,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:36:14.000Z","msg":"國際法權威及美國信譽何在<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52fbd26569f8d7790cfbe9f4e6f5861cf76aa9ff","tid":2168240,"uid":101845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:36:50.000Z","msg":"邊你咩事"},{"pid":"6d99d55ea367af99bef8648cf1b45b8d0cbc3c84","tid":2168240,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:38:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b54a44550008dcd41aa1c415eaf128b8f6e81cf","tid":2168240,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:38:57.000Z","msg":"原來伊朗核協議係聯合國攪出台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我都唔知"},{"pid":"5bd87f9d87742bcd5c003e718fc6b24340da13d7","tid":2168240,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T01:19:19.000Z","msg":"中國 伊朗 巴基斯坦 敍利亞 <br />\n<br />\n遲啲可能加埋土耳其"},{